--- Additional Definitions ---
Military Use includes:
- Development or operation of weapons systems
- Surveillance systems used for warfare
- Logistics or infrastructure supporting military operations
- Any application intended to inflict harm or enable military superiority

Acceptable Civilian Use includes:
- Humanitarian applications
- Civilian research
- Education
- Healthcare
- Environmental protection
